            "body": "Code looks good with one suggestion:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nString output = DockerCommandExecutor.executeDockerCommand(\r\n            pullCommand, Long.toHexString(System.currentTimeMillis()),\r\n            null, privOpExecutor, false, localizer.nmContext);\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nIn this context, there is no container id, maybe we can fix preparePrivilegedOperation to accept null instead of passing system time to make this more readable.",
